Author: Flesh-And-Bone
Text: don't feel guilty it just happens sometimes

Author: LisichkaYenotik
Text: Don't purge if you can help it.  &#x200B;  One binge is one binge. It is one slip up. One day. One tiny segment of your life. No one can say that they haven't eaten too much/binged/whatever you want to call it. You're human.   &#x200B;  There is always tomorrow. Draw a line under it. Learn from it. Think how it makes you feel. You got this. <3
